data.description: Looking for a totally upgraded SMART HOME w/ all the bells & whistles, look no further!! From the location (close to the Seminole Hard Rock Hotel) Private back yard, heated pool, outside shower, Tiki Hut & 3 outside TV’s (included) you don’t want to miss this one. This home is perfect for entertaining or just relaxing w/ the family. Entering the electric gate, glancing at the turf front yard you will instantly feel at home. If you prefer grass, no problem. Sprinkler lines are in place & can be activated. There is Porcelain tile throughout, granite counter tops in kitchen, Samsung appliances as well as a state-of-the-art security system. The new roof,  impact windows & doors are a HUGE plus w/ the rising cost of insurance in Florida.  Bring your best client, this property won’t disappoint!!
